Name: Nautilus Strike
Desc:
Orders the Nautilus to attack multiple enemies at once. The Nautilus does not cause you to take damage even when attacking enemies in the Damage Reflection Status.
Increases Majestic Presence's Final Damage with the Captain's majesty.Lv. 30 Effect: Can learn the 5th Advancement Skill, Nautilus Assault.
